C                             (1-THETA*BETA)**3
C
C              THIS DISTRIBUTION IS SOMETIMES PARAMETERIZED USING
C              THE MEAN (MU) INSTEAD OF THETA.  THIS RESULTS IN
C              THE PROBABILITY MASS FUNCTION:
