C                  (BETA*X-1  X)*((MU-1)/(BETA*MU-1))**(X-1)*
C                  (MU*(BETA-1)/(BETA*MU-1))**(BETA*X-X)/(BETA*X-1)
C                  X = 1, 2, 3, ,...
