C     OTHER DATAPAC   SUBROUTINES NEEDED--FZERO.
C     FORTRAN LIBRARY SUBROUTINES NEEDED--NONE.
C     MODE OF INTERNAL OPERATIONS--DOUBLE PRECISION.
C     LANGUAGE--ANSI FORTRAN (1977)
