C              FUNCTION VALUE FOR THE TYPE 2 GENERALIZED LOGISTIC
C              DISTRIBUTION WITH SHAPE PARAMETER ALPHA.
C              THIS DISTRIBUTION IS DEFINED FOR ALL X
