C              F(X) = 1 - EXP(-ALPHA*X)/(1+EXP(-X))**ALPHA
C     INPUT  ARGUMENTS--DX     = THE DOUBLE PRECISION VALUE 
C                                AT WHICH THE PROBABILITY DENSITY
C                                FUNCTION IS TO BE EVALUATED.
C                     --DALPHA = THE DOUBLE PRECISION SHAPE
